{"tid":2139330,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"「市民基因不會送中」 - 馮睎乾","createTime":"2020-08-04T08:06:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-04T08:36:19.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e1c4be67a580504311e0b339cde2c173c53e8ce2","tid":2139330,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T08:06:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20200714/UL7KGMG6BRDNFEQDES72Q2HJKM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20200714%2FUL7KGMG6BRDNFEQDES72Q2HJKM%2F&d=dUSYmziiyXe0H9uVu%2B4Yd8kuRvkIHaPazTq7BlmTy1I%3D&h=4a47318f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20200714%2FUL7KGMG6BRDNFEQDES72Q2HJKM%2F&h=c9c70674\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20200714/UL7KGMG6BRDNFEQDES72Q2HJKM/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n「市民基因不會送中」 - 馮睎乾<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/LIh3Z_dvBSUR6F6_i8_qeKYs3Jg=/3971x2731/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/U4TOMEQG25EH7FA7QASSU7QSBA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FLIh3Z_dvBSUR6F6_i8_qeKYs3Jg%3D%2F3971x2731%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FU4TOMEQG25EH7FA7QASSU7QSBA.jpg&h=06a3d6f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n特區政府高調闢謠，。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n友人說：「我中文真係麻麻，淨係聽過鬼佬講『Never believe anything until it is officially denied』，咁你話信唔信政府好？」我答：「梗係信。𠵱家我每朝起身都向基本法裝三炷香，而根據基本法神聖嘅第一條：『香港特別行政區是中華人民共和國不可分離的部分』，再加上有偉大嘅國安法庇佑，就知道香港又好大陸又好，咪一樣係中國，不用分那麼細。既然所有嘢都可以喺香港做，點解要送中呢？人驚你又驚，你知送中做乜咩？」<br />\n<br />\n友人說：「Er⋯⋯係喎，送中做乜？」我說：「有謠言話，係好似新疆咁做『DNA表型分析』吖嘛。」「咩嚟㗎？」「即係用一個人嘅基因資料重構佢嘅面譜，方便識別罪犯，加強社會監控。」友人馬上說：「吓？咁香港唔可以做分析咩？政府否認送中咋喎，冇否認會做分析。」我豎起大拇指稱讚：「你都蠢唔晒。冇錯，政府咁講，原理就好似梁振英話老婆放棄英國護照，但冇話放棄英國國籍一樣&mdash;&mdash;唔放棄國籍，隨時可以續領護照㗎嘛。」<br />\n<br />\n友人說：「X，咁我唔做啦！」我搖頭嘆息：「唉，一日最衰都係政府，淨係識同市民講唔會。。。。。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"8c467a21a87ddf5be936bc61718d99a9db62bad1","tid":2139330,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T08:08:13.000Z","msg":"香港警察是可靠證人"},{"pid":"5518e8e13f3a6af2fc3f8d7c4e4007e60d373436","tid":2139330,"uid":192517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T08:11:12.000Z","msg":"啲去氧核糖核酸梗係唔會送啦<br />\n送資料姐嘛"},{"pid":"c14f1851cb13dd810e4daac90391a798c8823047","tid":2139330,"uid":118870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e1c4be67a580504311e0b339cde2c173c53e8ce2","tid":2139330,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T08:06:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20200714/UL7KGMG6BRDNFEQDES72Q2HJKM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20200714%2FUL7KGMG6BRDNFEQDES72Q2HJKM%2F&d=dUSYmziiyXe0H9uVu%2B4Yd8kuRvkIHaPazTq7BlmTy1I%3D&h=4a47318f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20200714%2FUL7KGMG6BRDNFEQDES72Q2HJKM%2F&h=c9c70674\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20200714/UL7KGMG6BRDNFEQDES72Q2HJKM/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n「市民基因不會送中」 - 馮睎乾<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/LIh3Z_dvBSUR6F6_i8_qeKYs3Jg=/3971x2731/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/U4TOMEQG25EH7FA7QASSU7QSBA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FLIh3Z_dvBSUR6F6_i8_qeKYs3Jg%3D%2F3971x2731%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FU4TOMEQG25EH7FA7QASSU7QSBA.jpg&h=06a3d6f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n特區政府高調闢謠，。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n友人說：「我中文真係麻麻，淨係聽過鬼佬講『Never believe anything until it is officially denied』，咁你話信唔信政府好？」我答：「梗係信。𠵱家我每朝起身都向基本法裝三炷香，而根據基本法神聖嘅第一條：『香港特別行政區是中華人民共和國不可分離的部分』，再加上有偉大嘅國安法庇佑，就知道香港又好大陸又好，咪一樣係中國，不用分